on the forum were true.

153
00:12:01,065 --> 00:12:02,480
Han Yansheng dumped her.

154
00:12:03,000 --> 00:12:04,840
I never thought
they were a good match anyway.

155
00:12:04,920 --> 00:12:06,555
Getting dumped
was only a matter of time.

156
00:12:06,600 --> 00:12:08,466
