161
00:12:21,360 --> 00:12:23,120
You guys go ahead and eat.
I'm heading out.

162
00:12:33,120 --> 00:12:34,640
Let's pack her food for her.

163
00:12:50,035 --> 00:12:51,920
Jian Dan, come to the café right now.

164
00:12:52,200 --> 00:12:53,000
