168
00:13:05,520 --> 00:13:07,920
(Han Yansheng's condition
is getting worse.)

169
00:13:08,200 --> 00:13:09,680
(It might never get better.)

170
00:13:09,960 --> 00:13:12,840
(I feel more lost
and helpless than ever.)

171
00:13:13,200 --> 00:13:15,880
(Maybe I should give up.)

172
00:13:18,134 --> 00:13:20,920
(I should tell him I don't love him)

173
00:13:21,200 --> 00:13:23,200
