204
00:15:09,840 --> 00:15:11,400
(He lost all confidence)

205
00:15:11,680 --> 00:15:13,200
(and started giving up on himself.)

206
00:15:14,374 --> 00:15:16,948
(Thankfully, I woke up and realized)

207
00:15:17,111 --> 00:15:18,120
(it was just a dream.)

208
00:15:19,400 --> 00:15:20,920
(But I'm feeling uncertain now.)

209
00:15:21,600 --> 00:15:23,920
(I don't know if pushing him
to face his past trauma)

210
00:15:24,858 --> 00:15:26,280
(was the right thing to do.)

211
