(Yesterday,
I recommended a movie to him)

212
00:15:31,320 --> 00:15:32,600
(called "Good Will Hunting".)

213
00:15:33,447 --> 00:15:34,800
(The main character in it)

214
00:15:35,360 --> 00:15:37,840
(suffers from PTSD.)

215
00:15:39,360 --> 00:15:42,520
(He was abandoned as a child, abused,)

216
00:15:43,400 --> 00:15:46,360
