yet deeply insecure.)

217
00:15:47,066 --> 00:15:49,444
(He thought his girlfriend
didn't love him.)

218
00:15:49,640 --> 00:15:50,960
(That she wanted to leave him)

219
00:15:51,200 --> 00:15:52,160
(and break up with him.)

220
00:15:53,000 --> 00:15:55,800
(In the end,
with the help of a professor,)

221
00:15:56,320 --> 00:15:58,000
(he overcame his trauma,)

222
00:15:58,480 --> 00:15:59,800
(reconciled with his girlfriend,)

223
00:16:00,320 --> 00:16:01,977
(and started a new life.)

224
00:16:02,400 --> 00:16:04,160
(I hoped the film)

225
00:16:04,555 --> 00:16:06,044
(would encourage Han Yansheng,)

226
00:16:06,880 --> 00:16:08,280
(but he didn't watch it.)

227
00:16:09,320 --> 00:16:10,866
(He's been in low spirits.)

228
00:16:11,920 --> 00:16:13,160
(I don't know)

229
00:16:13,440 --> 00:16:15,120
